931
01:19:32,200 --> 01:19:33,720
 Ono što ti tražiš,

932
01:19:33,720 --> 01:19:34,980
 to će te pronaći.

933
01:19:34,980 --> 01:19:36,700
 To je to,

934
01:19:36,700 --> 01:19:37,360
 pronaćiš te,

935
01:19:37,360 --> 01:19:38,360
 vrlo je jednostavno.

936
01:19:38,360 --> 01:19:38,940
 Jel?

937
01:19:38,940 --> 01:19:41,560
 I onda sam ja, eto,

938
01:19:41,560 --> 01:19:43,180
 shvatila da je to,

939
01:19:43,180 --> 01:19:45,260
 možda je to to moje otkrivenje,

940
01:19:45,260 --> 01:19:46,160
 otvorila sam oči.

941
01:19:46,160 --> 01:19:47,160
 Ako nikoga nema,

942
01:19:47,160 --> 01:19:47,980
 ako sam ja ta,

943
01:19:47,980 --> 01:19:49,740
 što kaže ovaj mišak,

944
01:19:49,740 --> 01:19:50,320
 to mi je super,

945
01:19:50,320 --> 01:19:52,080
 kod njega i tu mi je isto malo on otvorio,

946
01:19:52,080 --> 01:19:53,100
 non-playing character

947
01:19:53,100 --> 01:19:54,000
 i playing character.

948
01:19:54,400 --> 01:19:54,740
 dobro,

949
01:19:54,740 --> 01:19:55,840
 to je sad malo isto dublje,

950
01:19:55,840 --> 01:19:56,080
 ali,

951
01:19:56,080 --> 01:19:57,400
 ako sam ja ta,

952
01:19:57,400 --> 01:19:58,780
 i to je u budizmu isto,

953
01:19:58,780 --> 01:19:59,820
 što ti kažeš,

954
01:19:59,820 --> 01:20:00,740
 oni po religiji,

955
01:20:00,740 --> 01:20:01,660
 Buda je govorio,

956
01:20:01,660 --> 01:20:02,200
 nema Boga,

957
01:20:02,200 --> 01:20:03,000
 imaš samo ti,

958
01:20:03,000 --> 01:20:03,920
 sebe,

959
01:20:03,920 --> 01:20:04,600
 ali zapravo,

960
01:20:04,600 --> 01:20:05,600
 to je Bog.

961
01:20:06,140 --> 01:20:07,320
 ne kao ti si Bog,

962
01:20:07,320 --> 01:20:10,020
 ova naša 3D ego varijanta,

963
01:20:10,020 --> 01:20:12,100
 ali ti si taj koji kreiraš sve,

964
01:20:12,100 --> 01:20:12,900
 jel?

965
01:20:12,900 --> 01:20:13,940
 Sve što jest.

966
01:20:13,940 --> 01:20:15,800
 Drugo je što ti treba utjehla,

967
01:20:15,800 --> 01:20:16,020
 aha,

968
01:20:16,020 --> 01:20:16,880
 bit ću dobar ovdje,

969
01:20:16,880 --> 01:20:18,720
 pa ću otići kod nekog brata,

970
01:20:18,720 --> 01:20:20,300
 tog čovjeka na oblak se sjesti,

971
01:20:20,300 --> 01:20:21,900
 on će mi govori da me voli za ovijek.

972
01:20:21,900 --> 01:20:23,480
 Ja to razumijem da ljudi trebaju

973
01:20:23,480 --> 01:20:25,080
 i ne rugam se s ovime,

974
01:20:25,080 --> 01:20:25,240
 jel?

975
01:20:25,240 --> 01:20:26,260
 Nije mi to cilj,

976
01:20:26,260 --> 01:20:28,100
 ali razumijem da to ljudima treba,

977
01:20:28,100 --> 01:20:29,060
 ali to su sve samo,

978
01:20:29,060 --> 01:20:29,840
 again,

979
01:20:29,840 --> 01:20:32,320
 priče za laku noć.

980
01:20:33,780 --> 01:20:35,000
 I ne znam što sam još htjela reći,

981
01:20:35,000 --> 01:20:36,500
 ali odletle su mi misli.

982
01:20:36,500 --> 01:20:40,960
 Često mi zvoni jedan citat,

983
01:20:40,960 --> 01:20:43,880
 sad zapravo,

984
01:20:43,880 --> 01:20:45,420
 kad kažeš poslala si mail

985
01:20:45,420 --> 01:20:46,600
 i sad se ovo desilo,

986
01:20:46,600 --> 01:20:49,700
 ili si napravila neku drugu akciju,

987
01:20:49,700 --> 01:20:50,840
 znači nisi sjedila,

988
01:20:50,840 --> 01:20:51,640
 nisi čekala,

989
